<title>Bozbala shaq ótti endi, ketti senderden РӘЖ208</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.     Am               Dm               Am
 Bozbala shaq ótti endi, ketti senderden,
.Am        Dm                  Am
 Qol bulǵaıdy jańa ómir, bıik belderden.

[C1]
.     Dm
   Qadamdaryń qutty bolsyn!
.     Am
   Bastaryńa baqyt qonsyn!
.      Dm                      E7
   Jas otaýda bir bolyńdar Táńirmen.

[V2]
 Táńirdiń bergen batasyn saqtańdar máńgi,
 Qos júrek birge aıtsyn taýsylmas ándi.

[V3]
 Jetekshi bolsyn ómirde Jaratqan Ózi,
 Júrekterińde jazylsyn kıeli sózi.</lyrics>
